Robot Arm Examples
===============================================================================

Robot arm examples live with the host crate.

1. CLI-style demo
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
hosts/robot-arm/examples/robot-arm-demo/
  demo.mcfg
  demo.mec
```

This demo exercises robot command and state contexts without browser UI.

2. Browser demo
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
hosts/robot-arm/examples/browser-robot-arm-demo/
  demo.js
  demo.mcfg
  demo.mec
```

This demo connects the robot arm host model to a browser demo surface.

3. Guide
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See:

```text
docs/guides/robot-arm-demo.mec
```
